    <summary>Touch-friendly RSS/Atom reader</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Syndic is a simple, responsive feed reader designed for casual browsing.</p>
        <p>It is designed to adapt to either mouse and touch input, and run well on both desktop and mobile devices.</p>
        <p>The UI is designed with Plasma Desktop and Android in mind, but it should run in other environments as well.</p>
